# straylight — operator-supplied overrides. Copy to `.env` (gitignored) and
# fill in. The Vagrantfile and azure/scripts/az700.sh read vagrant/.env; the
# shell environment takes precedence over these values.
#
# ── AZ-700 track (azure/ + az700-* walkthroughs) ────────────────────────────
# AZURE_SUBSCRIPTION_ID — subscription GUID the az700.sh driver is allowed to
#                         deploy into. The driver refuses to run against any
#                         other active subscription (the "accidentally
#                         deployed to the work subscription" guard). No
#                         secrets: auth is interactive `az login`.
# AZ700_LOCATION        — Azure region for lab deployments (default centralus).
AZURE_SUBSCRIPTION_ID=
AZ700_LOCATION=
